 "name": "RPlog_Mind_The_Stacks",
 "title": "Mind the Stacks",
 "summary": "In the vast vertical archives of a library, Senator Tokoga recognizes the medic Myiari and the older newcomer Rainier, who had met in the park, and ambles over to join them. Myiari, who dislikes the research her job demands, grumbles about being stuck in the stacks, while Rainier sneaks snacks and fetches a datapad of his own. Over tea, the three trade easy conversation about their work, the burdens of public office, and what drew each of them to their professions, Tokoga reminiscing about his reluctant entry into the Senate. The relaxed encounter deepens the acquaintance between the three.",
